**/*.log
**/logs/

# Playwright browser downloads & cache
**/playwright-downloads/
**/.playwright/
server/node_modules/.cache/

# Cloudinary temp uploads / local caches
**/uploads/
**/tmp/

# Git internals
.git/

# Misc
**/*.map
